### Ordering

Name       | Type   | Description
---------- | -----  | -----------
`order_by` | String | `net_price` (default) or `final_price` (includes shipping & payment_method cost).

### Filtering

You may supply the optional parameter `include_meta[]=filters`
to get meta information about the filters that can be applied.

<%= render_code_from_file "api/product_filters" %>

### Applying filters

Name                | Type    | Description
----------          | -----   | -----------
`size`              | String  | ex: `40` Sizes of 40 up to (but not including) 41 will be returned
`distance`          | String  | ex: `2` Only products within 2km's will be returned
`availability`      | String  | ex: `0` Only products with immediate availability will be returned
`zero_installments` | Boolean | ex: `true` Only products with zero commission installments will be returned

